title: Volks World - May 2016
description:
English | 100 pages | PDF | 39 MB

VolksWorld is Britain's best-selling magazine dedicated to the whole air-cooled VW scene and a must-buy for all fans of the legendary vehicles, particularly the iconic Beetle. VolksWorld takes pride in going to extraordinary lengths to bring its readers the most outstanding and fascinating features packed full of the very best photography and information that cannot be found anywhere else. VolksWorld also reaches into exhibitions with the annual VolksWorld Show, the largest in-door VW event in the world
